This is a custom distribution of OIS (Object Oriented Input Library System),
version 1.4.

This distribution includes a custom XMake-based build system.


License
-------

OIS's license is unchanged: this library is released under the zlib/libpng License.

The license of OIS is contained in the file 'COPYING'.


Submodules
----------

This distribution use XMake as a GIT submodule. To download it, do:

    $ git submodule init
    $ git submodule update


Compilation
-----------

It is recommended to compile the library in a separate folder. Here's how I do it:

    $ mkdir build
    $ cd build
    $ cmake ..
    $ make
